OL,3,CMan, 68, charged with raping 37-year-
OL,4,Cold woman
OL,6,FA 68-year old man has been charged
OL,7,Fwith raping a woman in her thirties in
OL,8,FWest Sussex.
OL,10,FStephen Robinson is accused of
OL,11,Fcommitting the offence in Salvington
OL,12,FRoad in Durrington near Worthing, just
OL,13,Fbefore 6pm on Thursday, May 7th.
OL,15,FThe victim, a 37-year-old woman, has
OL,16,Freceived specialist safeguarding
OL,17,Fsupport as detectives continue to
OL,18,Finvestigate the circumstances.
