OL,3,CMan, 68, charged with raping 37-year-
OL,4,Cold woman
OL,6,FRobinson, of Cheviot Road, was
OL,7,Fremanded in custody and after an
OL,8,Finitial hearing at Brighton
OL,9,FMagistrates Court, was remanded to
OL,10,Fappear again before Lewes Crown Court
OL,11,Fon June 8th.
